com.versant.var.transport
Interface VARITransport

public interface VARITransport

This is the transport interface used by the replication sender and the receiver to get send and receive end points respectively.

getSendEndPoint

VARIEndPoint getSendEndPoint(java.util.Properties props)
Description copied from interface: VARITransport
Get the send end point. Used by the replcation sender to get a send end point.
It takes java.util.Properties as an argument. It can be used to pass in properties such as address to be used to create/get a send end point. The following properties are passed in by the replication sender: Key: VARITransport.ADDRESS ("address"), value: Stringified address.
